<plot>OUR SUMMER MOVIE follows the adventures of a group of college students who spend their summer spoofing the film industry and living the high life of successful filmmakers. Tony Greco, a third year film student, is talented but not particularly dedicated. When his little town of Woodland Falls is snubbed by a Hollywood production company shooting "The Seventh Sense", Tony dreads another boring summer of working in his dad's hardware store. He and his friends devise a crazy plan to spend their summer as filmmakers, reaping all the benefits of their newfound power and celebrity, until a random intersection with a film executive threatens to bring their elaborate plot crashing down.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?417732</url></doc>
